data.description: SELLER WILL PAY $10,000 TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS OR TO BUY DOWN THE INTEREST RATE UPON A FULL PRICE OFFER! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence boasts an abundance of natural light create an airy and inviting atmosphere! Step into the wide foyer and vast living space with elevated tray ceilings. The heart of this home is the spacious living room open to the kitchen complete with a large island, ample cabinet space, and granite countertop, and modern appliances. Each of the four bedrooms offer ample space. The walk-in closets provide convenient storage solutions, ensuring that everyone has plenty of room for their belongings. The main suite is a true retreat, featuring a garden tub for soaking away the stresses of the day, a spacious shower, a private toilet closet, and a linen closet. The guest bathroom is generously sized, offering both style and convenience for your visitors. Step outside and discover your own outdoor haven. The large front yard and backyard welcomes you with lush, new grass! In the backyard, entertain guests in style on the screened-in porch, ideal for enjoying the outdoors without the hassle of bugs. The extended patio provides the perfect space for gatherings, making it an excellent spot for summer barbecues and cozy evenings under the stars. The backyard is expansive and fully fenced! Fanning Bayou also offers a luxury style community pool, hot tub, and a playground for you and your guests to enjoy!
